      <title>中印同意进一步谈判解决边界争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-india-agree-on-more-talks-to-resolve-border-disputes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和印度同意举行进一步的外交会谈，以解决长期存在的边界争端，这一争端导致这两个拥有核武器的亚洲邻国之间的关系陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/china-india-agree-on-more-talks-to-resolve-border-disputes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:49:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
